description.en:
There are a lot of Sports & Fitness experts around us, but their experience has not  been well-known so far. So we want to build an ecosystem where fitness experts  can grow and get diverse supports and monetize their unique exercise content. 
This will result in a variety of content and influencers, and will also increase the interaction with our service users and sports companies.
